### ========================================
### Auth — ParkApp API
### ========================================
### Instrucciones:
### 1. Instalá la extensión "REST Client" en VS Code
### 2. Hacé click en "Send Request" arriba de cada bloque
### 3. Primero ejecutá el Login, copiá el token y pegalo en @token

@host = http://localhost:3000
@token = ACÁ_PEGÁ_TU_TOKEN

### -----------------------------------------
### 1. Login (admin)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### 2. Login — password incorrecto (401)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "incorrecta"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### 3. Login — campos vacíos (400)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
}

### -----------------------------------------
### 4. Register — sin token (401)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operador1",
  "password": "op123"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### 5. Register — con token admin (201)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "operador1",
  "password": "op123"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### 6. Register — username duplicado (409)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "operador1",
  "password": "op123"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### 7. Register — role inválido (400)
### -----------------------------------------

POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "otro",
  "password": "123",
  "role": "superadmin"
}

### -----------------------------------------
### 8. Health check
### -----------------------------------------

GET {{host}}/health
